### Create Entry - Individual athlete in Swimming 400m Freestyle
POST {{host}}/api/entries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "1234567",
  "eventRsc": "SWMW400MFR------------",
  "competitorType": "Individual",
  "organisation": "USA"
}

### Create Entry - Team entry in Judo Mixed Team
POST {{host}}/api/entries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "2345678",
  "eventRsc": "JUDXTEAM--------------",
  "competitorType": "Team",
  "organisation": "JAM",
  "category": "Mixed",
  "teamId": "JUDXTEAM------JAM01"
}

### Get Entry by ID
GET {{host}}/api/entries/1234567_SWMW400MFR----------------------------
Accept: application/json

### Get Entry (not found)
GET {{host}}/api/entries/nonexistent_entry
Accept: application/json

### List Entries by RSC prefix (event level - all entries for SWM W 400MFR)
GET {{host}}/api/entries/by-rsc/SWMW400MFR
Accept: application/json

### List Entries by RSC prefix (discipline level - all SWM entries)
GET {{host}}/api/entries/by-rsc/SWM
Accept: application/json

### Change Entry Status - Activate
PATCH {{host}}/api/entries/1234567_SWMW400MFR----------------------------/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": "Active"
}

### Change Entry Status - Invalid transition (Active -> Entered)
PATCH {{host}}/api/entries/1234567_SWMW400MFR----------------------------/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": "Entered"
}

### Withdraw Entry
POST {{host}}/api/entries/1234567_SWMW400MFR----------------------------/withdraw

### Validation: missing participantId
POST {{host}}/api/entries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "",
  "eventRsc": "SWMW400MFR------------",
  "competitorType": "Individual",
  "organisation": "USA"
}

### Validation: invalid competitorType
POST {{host}}/api/entries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "9999999",
  "eventRsc": "SWMW400MFR------------",
  "competitorType": "InvalidType",
  "organisation": "USA"
}
